        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3682242297" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer11037862471712205000"> Mrs. Pollifax rarely disappoints! This mission to China is as exciting and well-crafted a story as I&apos;ve come to expect from the series. Having a tour group as the main cast of characters was a smart choice; it made for some unusual group tensions and dynamics. Of the side characters Iris is definitely the most fun to read about, and she&apos;s a great example of Gilman&apos;s knack for wonderful characterization. <br/><br/> The settings are described richly and with a sense of awe. I don&apos;t know if Dorothy Gilman e</span>
  <span id="freeText11037862471712205000" style="display:none"> Mrs. Pollifax rarely disappoints! This mission to China is as exciting and well-crafted a story as I've come to expect from the series. Having a tour group as the main cast of characters was a smart choice; it made for some unusual group tensions and dynamics. Of the side characters Iris is definitely the most fun to read about, and she's a great example of Gilman's knack for wonderful characterization. <br /><br /> The settings are described richly and with a sense of awe. I don't know if Dorothy Gilman ever visited China herself, but she makes the landscapes and culture sound fascinating. I look forward to completing the series to see if the rest have the same addictive blend of charm and suspense as <i>Mrs. Pollifax on the China Station</i>.</span>
  <a data-text-id="11037862471712205000" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


